message.body: What's up stranger!?
I'm at the chiropractor :-(
U ok?
U know I got back problems right
Yea but I didn't know it was bad
yup
Wassup with u
Nothing much at all lol
Doin anything dun for memorial day?
Prob jus BBQ'n here.. My kid broke her nose yesterday so I'm afraid to let her leave the house bc it's just a small fracture and the doc said to be careful bc she didn't want it to crack anymore
Wyd?
Idk just chill in nothing big I guess. How'd she break it

She climbed up on the counter and fell and when she fell she banged her face on the stool.. I was in the bthrm I heard her fall and scream I knew she broke something bc it was the same scream from when she broke her leg smh.. I thought it was her knee bc
Damn two bones already
That's the 3rd lol
dam she need milk
I think she broke her arm and her leg so young and easily bc she was allergic to milk then.. But yesterday I can see how that broke lol
U gotta lower the cookies or whatever she was tryna get
Lol she was trying to get her wallet lol
Yeah she def needed that money. Is Ur back better??
Not really and my hips have been bothering me the past few days.. I need to stop wearing uggs and flip flops but they're my life! Lol!
U ever do anything about Ur back?
Not really lol my doc suggested me wearing sneakers.. Smh
Gotta get those Dr scholls. I hope this chiropractor works. I'm runnin out ta options
Do U just get adjusted?
Idk that was my first time. But yeah he cracked the shit outta my spine
I got adjusted when I was pregnant with Tay I was scared for my life lol
Did it help?
I didn't do it bc I had a prob.. I worked at a chiropractors office and we had to get adjusted every 2 wks
Why did u have too? That was part of the job?? Lol
Lol I guess.. How could we tell patients about adjusting if we never had it five
Done*%
U ain't the dr
What do u think of it in general
Idk.. I didn't really care too much for it
Lol what do patients seem to think. Anybody find success with it??
But that just my opinion.. My gf swears by it
For real. Yeah I always kinda thought it was a pseudo science. But I'm getting desperate. Yoga the last straw lol
You either love it or hate it.. I used to get embarrassed telling people I worked in a chiropractors office bc a lot of people don't believe in them lol
And the patients we had come in thought he docs were gods ..
Hmmm were they all kooky ppl
Yea! They brought their dogs in to get adjusted, newborn babies.. Smh
Oh wtf. Ur doctors did dogs and shit?
Yea lol
They can't be certified for that lol
